# ==========================================
# Docker Build Context Exclusions
# ==========================================
# Whitelist approach: exclude everything, then allow only what the build needs.
# Additional exclusions below are defense-in-depth alongside the whitelist.

*
!pom.xml
!src/

# Defense-in-depth exclusions (redundant with whitelist but explicit)
target/
.git/
.github/
.githooks/
.opencode/
.idea/
*.iws
*.iml
*.md
config/
.env
.env.*
.gitleaks.toml
.gitignore
.gitattributes
